verses.text_plain: And the Lord spake unto Moses, saying,
verses.verse_html: 1And the Lord spake unto Moses, saying,

verses.text_plain: Command the children of Israel, and say unto them, When ye come into the land of Canaan; (this is the land that shall fall unto you for an inheritance, even the land of Canaan with the coasts thereof:)
verses.verse_html: 2Command the children of Israel, and say unto them, When ye come into the land of Canaan; (this is the land that shall fall unto you for an inheritance, even the land of Canaan with the coasts thereof:)

verses.text_plain: Then your south quarter shall be from the wilderness of Zin along by the coast of Edom, and your south border shall be the outmost coast of the salt sea eastward:
verses.verse_html: 3Then your south quarter shall be from the wilderness of Zin along by the coast of Edom, and your south border shall be the outmost coast of the salt sea eastward:

verses.text_plain: And your border shall turn from the south to the ascent of Akrabbim, and pass on to Zin: and the going forth thereof shall be from the south to Kadesh–barnea, and shall go on to Hazar–addar, and pass on to Azmon:
verses.verse_html: 4And your border shall turn from the south to the ascent of Akrabbim, and pass on to Zin: and the going forth thereof shall be from the south to Kadesh–barnea, and shall go on to Hazar–addar, and pass on to Azmon:

tokens.text: thereof shall be from the south

verses.text_plain: And the border shall fetch a compass from Azmon unto the river of Egypt, and the goings out of it shall be at the sea.
verses.verse_html: 5And the border shall fetch a compass from Azmon unto the river of Egypt, and the goings out of it shall be at the sea.

tokens.text: of it shall be at the sea

verses.text_plain: And as for the western border, ye shall even have the great sea for a border: this shall be your west border.
verses.verse_html: 6And as for the western border, ye shall even have the great sea for a border: this shall be your west border.

tokens.text: ye shall even have the great

verses.text_plain: And this shall be your north border: from the great sea ye shall point out for you mount Hor:
verses.verse_html: 7And this shall be your north border: from the great sea ye shall point out for you mount Hor:

tokens.text: And this shall be your north

verses.text_plain: From mount Hor ye shall point out your border unto the entrance of Hamath; and the goings forth of the border shall be to Zedad:
verses.verse_html: 8From mount Hor ye shall point out your border unto the entrance of Hamath; and the goings forth of the border shall be to Zedad:

verses.text_plain: And the border shall go on to Ziphron, and the goings out of it shall be at Hazar–enan: this shall be your north border.
verses.verse_html: 9And the border shall go on to Ziphron, and the goings out of it shall be at Hazar–enan: this shall be your north border.

tokens.text: of it shall be at Hazar–enan

verses.text_plain: And ye shall point out your east border from Hazar–enan to Shepham:
verses.verse_html: 10And ye shall point out your east border from Hazar–enan to Shepham:

verses.text_plain: And the coast shall go down from Shepham to Riblah, on the east side of Ain; and the border shall descend, and shall reach unto the side of the sea of Chinnereth eastward:
verses.verse_html:
11And the coast shall go down from Shepham to Riblah, on the east side of Ain; and the border shall descend, and shall reach unto the side of the sea of Chinnereth eastward: ▼
▼ side of the sea: Heb. shoulder of the sea

footnotes.body_text: ▼ side of the sea: Heb. shoulder of the sea
footnotes.body_html: ▼ side of the sea: Heb. shoulder of the sea

verses.text_plain: And the border shall go down to Jordan, and the goings out of it shall be at the salt sea: this shall be your land with the coasts thereof round about.
verses.verse_html: 12And the border shall go down to Jordan, and the goings out of it shall be at the salt sea: this shall be your land with the coasts thereof round about.

tokens.text: of it shall be at the salt

verses.text_plain: And Moses commanded the children of Israel, saying, This is the land which ye shall inherit by lot, which the Lord commanded to give unto the nine tribes, and to the half tribe:
verses.verse_html: 13And Moses commanded the children of Israel, saying, This is the land which ye shall inherit by lot, which the Lord commanded to give unto the nine tribes, and to the half tribe:

verses.text_plain: For the tribe of the children of Reuben according to the house of their fathers, and the tribe of the children of Gad according to the house of their fathers, have received their inheritance; and half the tribe of Manasseh have received their inheritance:
verses.verse_html: 14For the tribe of the children of Reuben according to the house of their fathers, and the tribe of the children of Gad according to the house of their fathers, have received their inheritance; and half the tribe of Manasseh have received their inheritance:

verses.text_plain: The two tribes and the half tribe have received their inheritance on this side Jordan near Jericho eastward, toward the sunrising.
verses.verse_html: 15The two tribes and the half tribe have received their inheritance on this side Jordan near Jericho eastward, toward the sunrising.

verses.text_plain: And the Lord spake unto Moses, saying,
verses.verse_html: 16And the Lord spake unto Moses, saying,

verses.text_plain: These are the names of the men which shall divide the land unto you: Eleazar the priest, and Joshua the son of Nun.
verses.verse_html: 17These are the names of the men which shall divide the land unto you: Eleazar the priest, and Joshua the son of Nun.

verses.text_plain: And ye shall take one prince of every tribe, to divide the land by inheritance.
verses.verse_html: 18And ye shall take one prince of every tribe, to divide the land by inheritance.

verses.text_plain: And the names of the men are these: Of the tribe of Judah, Caleb the son of Jephunneh.
verses.verse_html: 19And the names of the men are these: Of the tribe of Judah, Caleb the son of Jephunneh.

verses.text_plain: And of the tribe of the children of Simeon, Shemuel the son of Ammihud.
verses.verse_html: 20And of the tribe of the children of Simeon, Shemuel the son of Ammihud.

verses.text_plain: Of the tribe of Benjamin, Elidad the son of Chislon.
verses.verse_html: 21Of the tribe of Benjamin, Elidad the son of Chislon.

verses.text_plain: And the prince of the tribe of the children of Dan, Bukki the son of Jogli.
verses.verse_html: 22And the prince of the tribe of the children of Dan, Bukki the son of Jogli.

verses.text_plain: The prince of the children of Joseph, for the tribe of the children of Manasseh, Hanniel the son of Ephod.
verses.verse_html: 23The prince of the children of Joseph, for the tribe of the children of Manasseh, Hanniel the son of Ephod.

verses.text_plain: And the prince of the tribe of the children of Ephraim, Kemuel the son of Shiphtan.
verses.verse_html: 24And the prince of the tribe of the children of Ephraim, Kemuel the son of Shiphtan.

verses.text_plain: And the prince of the tribe of the children of Zebulun, Elizaphan the son of Parnach.
verses.verse_html: 25And the prince of the tribe of the children of Zebulun, Elizaphan the son of Parnach.

verses.text_plain: And the prince of the tribe of the children of Issachar, Paltiel the son of Azzan.
verses.verse_html: 26And the prince of the tribe of the children of Issachar, Paltiel the son of Azzan.

verses.text_plain: And the prince of the tribe of the children of Asher, Ahihud the son of Shelomi.
verses.verse_html: 27And the prince of the tribe of the children of Asher, Ahihud the son of Shelomi.

verses.text_plain: And the prince of the tribe of the children of Naphtali, Pedahel the son of Ammihud.
verses.verse_html: 28And the prince of the tribe of the children of Naphtali, Pedahel the son of Ammihud.

verses.text_plain: These are they whom the Lord commanded to divide the inheritance unto the children of Israel in the land of Canaan.
verses.verse_html: 29These are they whom the Lord commanded to divide the inheritance unto the children of Israel in the land of Canaan.
